Modules

Here is a list of all modules:
  • applLayer - application layer modules
  • netwLayer - network layer modules
  • nic - network interfaces
    • macLayer - MAC layer modules
    • phyLayer - physical layer modules
      • analogueModels - AnalogueModel implementations
      • decider - decider modules
  • mobility - modules handling the mobility of the hosts
  • utils - utiltity classes
  • base - base MiXiM modules
    • baseModules - base module classes of MiXiM
    • BaseUtility - blackboard related stuff
    • connectionManager - channel and connection related classes
    • baseUtils - utitities for base MiXiM
  • mapping - classes representing mathematical mappings
    • mappingDetails - mostly internal mapping classes
  • examples - Classes for the examples of MiXiM
    • AnalogueModels example - Classes from the AnalogueModels example
    • CSMAMac example - Classes from the CSMAMac example
  • Power consumption - Classes using/defining power consumption
